name: GachaAI
description: GachaAI is a Solana-based application that allows users to generate new memecoins on the pump.fun platform. Users adjust a set of sliders representing characteristics such as "Cuteness," "Professionalism," "Futuristic," "Boldness," and "Elegance" to define the attributes of their desired coin. Upon clicking the "ROLL" button and paying a fee of 0.025 SOL, GachaAI generates a memecoin based on the selected parameters.
